    <item>
      <title>由于通胀担忧，南非利率全年保持不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/south-african-rates-seen-on-hold-all-year-amid-inflation-worry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金融期货市场的押注显示，由于持续的通货膨胀，南非央行今年不会降息，甚至有可能提高利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/south-african-rates-seen-on-hold-all-year-amid-inflation-worry</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 12:37:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行第五次会议维持利率稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/ecb-holds-rates-steady-for-fifth-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周四将存款利率维持在创纪录的4%，同时发出明确信号，即通胀降温将很快允许其开始降息。莉兹·伯登 (Lizzy Burden) 接受彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-11/ecb-holds-rates-steady-for-fifth-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 12:34:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CFA 期末考试通过率升至 49%，低于十年平均水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/cfa-final-exam-pass-rate-rises-to-49-below-the-decade-average</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特许金融分析师考试最终级别的通过率保持在十年平均水平以下，而首次参加考试的人比选择推迟考试的人的成功率更高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/cfa-final-exam-pass-rate-rises-to-49-below-the-decade-average</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
