    <item>
      <title>债券交易员正在为 5% 的收益率、不降息的世界做准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/bond-traders-shift-thinking-to-a-5-yield-no-rate-cut-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储今年不降息的可能性越来越大，债券交易员正在为 10 年期美国国债收益率突破 5% 做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/bond-traders-shift-thinking-to-a-5-yield-no-rate-cut-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 07:40:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行保持利率稳定，交易商重新定价全球宽松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/german-bonds-drop-as-traders-pare-ecb-cut-bets-ahead-of-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国出乎意料的高通胀数据刺激全球货币政策前景迅速重新定价之后，交易员押注欧元区和英国今年降息的次数会更少且更慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/german-bonds-drop-as-traders-pare-ecb-cut-bets-ahead-of-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 07:40:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗袭击以色列的风险成为焦点，油价波动至90美元附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-11</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员继续关注伊朗或其代理人对以色列的潜在袭击，在连续几天的波动中，油价冷却了前一天的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-11</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:30:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PPI后库存波动；欧洲央行令欧元下跌：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新通胀数据低于预期后，股市波动，突显美联储在实现 2% 目标方面面临的坎坷道路。随着欧洲央行在 6 月份确定首次降息，欧元下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 22:45:34 GMT</pubDate>
